Package: vdr-plugin-dvdswitch
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${vdr:Depends}, vdr-plugin-dvd, eject, at
Suggests: dvd+rw-tools
Description: VDR plugin to create, burn, mount and manage DVD iso images
 With this VDR plugin it is possible to select between DVD iso images,
 directories containing a DVD file structure or the real DVD drive and
 mount them for playback with the DVD plugin. The Plugin allows also
 to create iso images from a DVD and or to burn them onto a DVD.
